						               													<description>Wanted: Igor! is a monster-building game in which players take turns playing cards in order to create as many creatures as possible under Dr. Frankenstein's orders.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;At the beginning of the game, a number of plan cards one less than the number of players are revealed. Players must connect body parts to the five different slots on the plans in order to complete the creatures, receiving a certain number of Marks for each body part placed. Once a creature is complete, the player with the most Marks on that creature gets credit for its creation and scores a victory point (VP). The completed creature is then discarded and replaced with a new plan card. Whoever first scores 4 VPs wins.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;     IndieCade 2014 Official Selection, Los Angeles, California&amp;#10;     Seal of Approval from The Dice Tower&amp;#10;     Best Sellable Board Game - Nordic Game Jam 2013, Copenhagen, Denmark&amp;#10;     Nominated for the People's Choice Award - Nordic Game Jam 2013, Copenhagen, Denmark&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
